  <brief_title>Efficacy of Copper in Reducing Health-Acquired Infections in a Pediatric Intensive Care Unit</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of Copper in Reducing Health-Acquired Infections and Microbial Burden as Measured on High Touch Surfaces in a Pediatric Intensive Care Unit. A Controlled Clinical Trial.</official_title>
